{"tid":386354,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"其實Asso比人笑，係因為一啲人做壞規矩","createTime":"2017-09-03T19:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T17:57:20.000Z","uid":90801,"like":432,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6365ddda2a5e5b4b2edaa847bdf7a1beb20370","tid":386354,"uid":90801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T19:58:59.000Z","msg":"成日都話一粒老鼠屎搞衰一鍋粥<br />\nAsso仔比人笑 比人串既原因係咩？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係冇自知之明</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你入得asso，你就要知道<br />\n自己係比人差 比人廢<br />\n你冇資格怪dse失手 因為你dse唔失手都入唔到u<br />\n<br />\n呢間學校只係你既踏腳石 <br />\n點解你又要去諗咩校園生活？<br />\n話識人好過識字，你諗下你asso識到既人會係咩人<br />\n<br />\n好啦講到最尾就算比你入返大學啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">何解你班戇鳩又係度打晒飛機？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n入大學呢件事，對直入既人黎講<br />\n係一件必然既事<br />\n對於你地打晒飛機呢件事 對佢地黎講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真係I don't give a fuck</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你應該自卑點解要靠人比多次機會先入到大學<br />\n你唔應該自豪你努力左兩年<br />\n因為人地Dse努力左三年<br />\n你應該諗下成間大學既人個個都勁過你<br />\n你又憑乜野打飛機你入返大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：asso入返大學 但真係睇唔過眼"},{"pid":"e164e98c5962e7b10624f6d717b433bd4091f604","tid":386354,"uid":31376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:27:23.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"46d71aa2fdbba3e78783b67668d5d0a0ba451589","tid":386354,"uid":135386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:57:24.000Z","msg":"中"},{"pid":"cb5200c1372e2e0fe59b1b92d98bb14042ea0d3d","tid":386354,"uid":55823,"like":76,"dislike":4,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T21:25:47.000Z","msg":"asso仔真係好煩 入到U周圍同人講<br />\n<br />\n慌死人地唔知你走後門咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e82940c93fda3ed0285553042d703c2ee8ea9c3","tid":386354,"uid":44073,"like":17,"dislike":42,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T21:28:15.000Z","msg":